{"tid":1979304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲主張成立獨立機制調查疫情如何爆發 交由世衛以外的獨立人士執行 目前最關鍵的問題是中國在疫情上的透明度","createTime":"2020-04-19T10:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T11:54:53.000Z","uid":125168,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"60b6da6dd7713eeacec00885bb619534efd9faaf","tid":1979304,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:30:07.000Z","msg":"澳洲主張成立獨立機制調查疫情如何爆發<br />\n1小時前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】澳洲外長佩恩認為，目前最關鍵的問題，是中國在疫情上的透明度，主張應設立獨立的審查機制，調查這場疫情是怎樣爆發。<br />\n<br />\n佩恩稱有關審查機制，要靠國際社會合作，並交由世衛組織以外的獨立人士執行；她又認為，疫情明顯是由武漢開始，而且很可能源自濕街市。<br />\n<br />\n佩恩表示經過今次疫情過後，中國及其夥伴，以至中國及澳洲的關係都會改變，但她無進一步說明，未來雙方關係會怎樣變化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=388230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388230&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWpugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=da713b57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388230&h=ab80f2ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=388230</a>"},{"pid":"26e76d6164adbd2562075fadc21a3c05b87d9cdb","tid":1979304,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"佩恩表示經過今次疫情過後，中國及其夥伴，以至中國及澳洲的關係都會改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6481899d016898d5fe307a86949fd76167902b0c","tid":1979304,"uid":187510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"獨立調查委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji